Варвар не разборчив в выборе целей - он счастлив поразить ближайшего врага, каким бы он ни был.
Лучник стреляет в ближайшую цель, даже через стены.
Гигант сначала атакует защитные постройки. Когда о них позаботятся, он направляется к тому, что осталось на поле битвы. Как большой парень, он может выдержать большой урон.
Волшебник бросает огненный шар в ближайшего врага. Если поблизости окажутся другие враги, они тоже получат свою долю огненного взрыва.
Принц атакует прямо вперед, нанося большой урон врагу, достаточно глупому, чтобы стоять на его пути ... если кто-то действительно встанет на его пути.
П.Е.К.К.А наносит большой урон ближайшему противнику. Из-за ее тяжелой брони она также может противостоять сильному вражескому огню.
Бомбардировщик сбрасывает бомбу на вражескую сторону поля боя, нанося дополнительный урон стенам. Из-за монотонных тренировок он может попасть только в точку, параллельную тому, где он стоит.
Гоблина в первую очередь привлекает золото, и он наносит двойной урон хранилищам золота. Когда хранилищ золота не осталось, он атакует ближайшего врага.
Малыш Дракон летает над полем битвы и атакует прямо через поле битвы, выдыхая огонь на всех врагов на своем пути.
Огненный шар, наносящий урон по площади 3x3.
Zap наносит урон и оглушает врагов на несколько ходов.
Бревно катится по полю битвы, нанося урон врагам на своем пути.
Ракета наносит очень большой урон одной цели.
Атакуйте одиночным отрядом с двойным уроном, не тратя свой ход!
Отведите отряд обратно в свои резервы. Войска полностью выздоравливают, прежде чем снова присоединиться к битве!
Поменяйте местами два соседних отряда или переместите отряд на пустой квадрат рядом с ним.
Атакуйте всеми войсками одного типа, независимо от их расположения на поле боя.

There seem to be more of these islands..
I wonder what treasures they hold..
We’ll see, but first we must find our friends.
Let’s explore the first one. Tap the island.
Ugh, my robe's all wet. I hate water.. And swimming.
Care to try with armor?\nI hope this doesn’t leave a stain…
And how can Barbarian run underwater?!
Guys, how about we focus on those Cannons?
Looks like he’s ready to go!\nTap Barbarian to attack!
Let me show what our group can do.
Tap us for a combo attack!
The bigger the group, bigger the combo bonus.
Let us show you a magic trick..
Tap us to to make the Cannons disappear.. with fire!
Watch out! Those Cannons look like they’re about to fire!
Numbers next to enemies count down to their next attack.
These Cannons will shoot at us after our turn!
Great work!\nTo the victor go the spoils!
This is what we.. ehm, acquired, from the level.
Here’s a summary of everything we gained.
If you’re unsure what something is, just tap it!
No more units will come into play.
We’ll lose if we run out of units.
Hey! Looks like we can use my favorite Spell!
Use the spell by tapping on the highlighted board.
Spells can only be used a limited number of times per battle.
Looks like we have enough Gold and Elixir for an upgrade!
On this page you can see all your Troops, Spells and Tactics.
Tap the unit you can upgrade.
Here you can see the unit's stats, items and what it costs to upgrade.
With stronger units, we’re able to win harder battles.
Also earlier battles will become easier, if you'd wish to replay them.
Press and hold on a unit to preview its attack
This works on enemies too! Good luck!
Press and hold on a unit to preview its attack
All the cool people use preview!
Looks like this chest unlocks when we beat all stages of an island!
Tap on the Chest to reveal the rewards inside!
Salutations!\nWe haven’t been properly introduced yet!
You can address me by my royal title, Prince.
Simple enough, he’ll run to the nearest enemy and hit them.
Then there’s me, the Prince. In my shining armor of course.
I do more damage, but this stubborn horse only goes forward!
(You never ask me to turn.. And what did she mean by “high horse”?)
On the ranged side, here’s the Archer.
She’ll shoot over walls at the nearest enemies. Never misses.
His fireballs do a little less damage each, but to a much larger area!
Each troop is different. It’s up to you to use them efficiently.
(You’re gonna need luck with this bunch.. )
Later stages are much more challenging…
But you only need to beat the first stage to unlock the next level!
Sometimes it’s better to move on than to get stuck.
Looks like you’ve found an item for your troops!
Items add special powers to your troops’ attacks.
Most powers only activate when the group is big enough.
These icons show if the item power can activate.
Looks like you're out of troops, but still have a spell left.
Take out an enemy if you can, as you might get loot from it.
Salutations!\nMight I inquire who you are?
The true\nGoblin King!\nExiled by my usurper brother!
Joke’s on him though!\nHe's still pestering villages on the continent..
..while I enjoy the bounty of these islands.\nNow fetch me lunch!
Lunch? You're asking us to get you lunch?\nHow about you eat lance!
Hah! No!\nIt takes more than that to defeat me!
Special Elixir of these Islands makes me powerful and—
Hey! I noticed that you haven’t used the Fireball spell to it’s full potential.
It’s often a good idea to use it early and on clumps of enemies!
Welcome to the League!\nTest your mettle in an endless battle!
Each Stage you clear rewards you with a Trophy and a Chest.
You fight on until you run out of Troops and Spells.
There’s also Special Buildings! Destroy these to fill your reserves.
Get the trophies and rise to the glorious top!
That thing is huge! The arms look like they might come off.
If we want to take it down, we need to focus on the body.
There’s that hunk of lava rock again.
Hey! Get down here and taste my lance!
(What’s with him and the lance eating?)
You better wait for it to land before you go charging in, Prince.
Hmm... Don’t Baby Dragons grow up to be, you know, Dragons?
Actually, I think it’s cute! It’s almost a shame to defeat it. Almost.
Your Energy is full! Time to battle!
Last chance to play League today!
